plugin.description:
@R---------------- AKM plugin loaded ---------------------------------------------- This plugin manages looted keys and existing keys on your keyring.
Automatically deduplicates existing keys on keyring. Puts freshly looted keys to the keyring if there's no such key yet. Drops duplicate looted keys on the ground unless they're melt-drop or cursed. --- Features below this line are not there yet --- Puts no-save keys to container before logout. Optionally puts keys without (keep) flag to container before logout. Puts "unkept" keys not used for areas in your Q/GQ/CP level range to container. Gets keys used for areas in your Q/GQ/CP level range from container.
@w Type @Gakm help@w for more information.
1.004 Fix deduplicating of freshly looted keys. Don't try to put keys with rot timer on keyring.
